highlights.text: “座右銘” by Kary Ng is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 76 spots at #88.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1553 days straight.
Terence Lam has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “夏日之子” is the highest at #16.
“流浪星球” by Keung To is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #2.
